 ease.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/58279-dentrix3.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/sC7hVDicSLrGwZ6Z3YVBf8.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"sC7hVDicSLrGwZ6Z3YVBf8","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/sC7hVDicSLrGwZ6Z3YVBf8.jpg","alt":""},"id":"8aa4813f-dc5e-4c26-9cbd-38b1fac6e1ca","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Handling patient insurance information can be a headache, but Dentrix makes the process simple. You can enter all payment information directly into Dentrix so all of the information you need can easily be located. If you utilize Dentrix’s eService PowerPay, you can process credit card and debit card transactions, as well. Additional eService options include an Insurance Manager and eClaims, which help streamline the insurance and claim submission processes.","Referral tracking becomes an effortless process with Dentrix. You can track exactly how your patients heard about your practice, whether it is from other dentists, current patients, online, ads or any other source. By tracking your patient referrals, you can improve your referral numbers and make it a more effective process.","In addition, this practice software includes a long list of clinical tools. You can create custom view for charts and personal information of each patient. You can write notes and even draw objects and figures on charts to make viewing easier. Treatment planning options are also included, and you can create a plan with just a few clicks of the mouse.","Dentrix also offers a Lab Case Manager. This tool allows you to create a case, send it directly to a lab and then track its status. This makes the prescription process simple and eliminates many frustrating steps."]},"id":"ae3db7a3-e54f-4fbd-b6f3-af5fa6ba935e","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Features"},"id":"a75b9a28-78d7-42a3-97af-4ce12706e709","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/q9FfGZyxqDZEYv3cCAguPj.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption